OL,3,CSickness benefits bill 'devastating',
OL,4,CStarmer says as he defends reforms
OL,6,FThe rising sickness and disability
OL,7,Fbenefits bill is "devastating" for the
OL,8,Fpublic finances and has "wreaked a
OL,9,Fterrible human cost", Sir Keir Starmer
OL,10,Fsaid after his Government announced a
OL,11,F#5 billion cut to welfare.
OL,13,FThe Government on Tuesday announced a
OL,14,Fraft of welfare measures it says will
OL,15,Fhelp bring more working age people
OL,16,Fback into jobs, and which will save
OL,17,Fthe taxpayer billions of pounds.
