OL,3,CSickness benefits bill 'devastating',
OL,4,CStarmer says as he defends reforms
OL,6,FAmong the most significant moves is
OL,7,Fthe tightening of eligibility for
OL,8,Fpersonal independence payments (Pip),
OL,9,Fa benefit aimed at helping those with
OL,10,Fdisability or long-term illness with
OL,11,Fincreased living costs.
OL,13,FHundreds of thousands of people are
OL,14,Fexpected to be affected by the changes
OL,15,Fto Pip eligibility, which are expected
OL,16,Fto account for the largest proportion
OL,17,Fof savings the Government hopes to
OL,18,Fmake.
