OL,3,CSickness benefits bill 'devastating',
OL,4,CStarmer says as he defends reforms
OL,6,FElsewhere, ministers will scrap the
OL,7,Fwork capability assessment for
OL,8,Funiversal credit, the test of whether
OL,9,Fsomeone can get incapacity benefit
OL,10,Fpayments based on their fitness for
OL,11,Fwork.
OL,13,FThis will be replaced by 2028 with a
OL,14,Fsingle assessment considering the
OL,15,Fimpact a person's disability has on
OL,16,Fdaily living, rather than their
OL,17,Ffitness to work.
