OL,3,CSickness benefits bill 'devastating',
OL,4,CStarmer says as he defends reforms
OL,6,F"But more importantly it has wreaked a
OL,7,Fterrible human cost. Young people shut
OL,8,Fout of the labour market at a
OL,9,Fformative age. People with complex
OL,10,Flong-term conditions, written off by a
OL,11,Fsingle assessment.
OL,13,F"People who want to return to work,
OL,14,Fyet can't access the support they
OL,15,Fneed. All this is happening at scale
OL,16,Fand it is indefensible."
OL,18,FAmong other measures to be taken by
OL,19,Fthe Government are:
